text: Oktyabr () is a rural locality (a village) in Churayevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 151 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Mishkino, 3 km from Churayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Oktyabr, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
